data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the Country Creek neighborhood! Built in 1997, this corner lot home has a lot to offer. A new hot water heater was installed in November 2023, a new refrigerator in 2021, new blinds in 2021, and the flooring is luxury vinyl wood. The primary suite is located on the main floor, the second floor has a landing overlooking the living area, and each floor has a full bathroom. Seller is providing a one-year home warranty. Right of First Refusal in place with current contingent offer. Ask your Real Estate Agent for more information!
